	<div class="author">
		June 30th 8:50am by <a href="http://sportsshow.comedycentral.com/author/sleighta/" title="Posts by Andrew Sleighter">Andrew Sleighter</a>	</div>
	
	<h2 class="permalink">
		<a href="http://sportsshow.comedycentral.com/2011/06/30/thanks-for-watching/">Thanks For Watching</a>
	</h2>
	
	<div class="entry">
		<p>Unfortunately this will be the last post on the blog. We hope you had a good time reading it.</p>
<p>Thanks to all the tweeters, readers, commenters and watchers who supported the show and the blog.</p>
<p>It was a lot of fun for us to do.</p>
<p>And to those of you who illegally downloaded the show&#8230;</p>
<p>See what happens?!</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
	</div>

