	<h2 class="permalink">
		<a href="http://sportsshow.comedycentral.com/2011/06/24/metta-world-peace/">Metta World Peace</a>
	</h2>
	
	<div class="entry">
		<p><a href="http://sportsshow.comedycentral.com/files/2011/06/ron-artest-peace-530x318.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-5426" title="ron-artest-peace-530x318" src="http://sportsshow.comedycentral.com/files/2011/06/ron-artest-peace-530x318-e1308931839319.jpg" alt="" width="410" height="246" /></a>Yes, it is true.</p>
<p>Ron Artest has officially filed to change his name to Metta World Peace.</p>
<p>Although Ron seems like a happier person these days, he is fresh of clothes lining J.J. Barea during the NBA playoffs.</p>
<p>Is there any better way to guarantee an assault arrest of Ron than by him changing his name to World Peace?</p>
<p>He&#8217;s really tempting the comedy gods here. I mean, we just had a genitals picture scandal from a guy named Weiner.</p>
<p>I give it three months before you hear the sentence, &#8220;Mr. World Peace, how do you plead?&#8221;</p>
<p>photo: <a href="http://larrybrownsports.com/basketball/ron-artest-trying-to-change-name-to-metta-world-peace/74050" target="_blank">Larry Brown Sports</a></p>
