	<h2 class="permalink">
		<a href="http://sportsshow.comedycentral.com/2011/06/22/buffalo-wild-wings-save-our-business-modelseason-campaign/">Buffalo Wild Wings Save Our Business Model/Season Campaign</a>
	</h2>
	
	<div class="entry">
		<p><object style="height: 300px; width: 410px"><param name="movie" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/JUP5LyFqwtI?version=3"><param name="allowFullScreen" value="true"><param name="allowScriptAccess" value="always"><embed src="http://www.youtube.com/v/JUP5LyFqwtI?version=3" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" allowfullscreen="true" allowScriptAccess="always" width="410" height="300"></object></p>
<p>Buffalo Wild Wings is offering six free chicken wings to anyone who signs its <a href="http://www.petitiononline.com/waitwhat/petition.html">online petition</a> to end the NFL lockout. </p>
<p>As a chicken wing serving sports bar, Buffalo Wild Wings is one of the many businesses that would be devastated by an NFL lockout. </p>
<p>Other businesses that stand to lose? Fantasy football sites, MRI clinics, and the NFL. </p>
	</div>

