		June 20th 2:02pm by <a href="http://sportsshow.comedycentral.com/author/sleighta/" title="Posts by Andrew Sleighter">Andrew Sleighter</a>	</div>
	
	<h2 class="permalink">
		<a href="http://sportsshow.comedycentral.com/2011/06/20/turn-that-cubs-game-down-so-michael-wilbon-can-sleep/">Turn That Cubs Game Down So Michael Wilbon Can Sleep</a>
	</h2>
	
	<div class="entry">
		<p><a href="http://sportsshow.comedycentral.com/files/2011/06/wilbon-sleeping-cubs.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-5389" title="wilbon-sleeping-cubs" src="http://sportsshow.comedycentral.com/files/2011/06/wilbon-sleeping-cubs-e1308592656230.jpg" alt="" width="410" height="239" /></a>Five good minutes. He just needs five good minutes.</p>
<p>Photo: <a href="http://bustedcoverage.com/2011/06/20/michael-wilbon-takes-son-to-first-cubs-game-falls-asleep-leaves-early-photos/" target="_blank">Busted Coverage</a></p>
	</div>

	<div class="tags">
		Tags: <h3><a href="http://sportsshow.comedycentral.com/tag/cubs-game/" rel="tag">CUbs game</a></h3>, <h3><a href="http://sportsshow.comedycentral.com/tag/fathers-day/" rel="tag">Fathers day</a></h3>, <h3><a href="http://sportsshow.comedycentral.com/tag/michael-wilbon/" rel="tag">Michael Wilbon</a></h3>, <h3><a href="http://sportsshow.comedycentral.com/tag/sleeping/" rel="tag">sleeping</a></h3>	</div>
	
